snippet.title: Sky Gamblers: Cold War Trailer
snippet.description:
Take part in the most charismatic era of modern warfare: The Cold War. Pilot the very first generations for jet fighters and be part of the hidden pages of history!  Follow a story driven campaign with great mission variety and save the world from nuclear devastation!

Download for iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/sky-gamblers-cold-war/id652041723?ls=1&mt=8
Download for OSX: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/sky-gamblers-cold-war/id652045920?ls=1&mt=12
